{"type":"message","id":"e3a57411","parentId":"a40aec58","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:01:54.502Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: [assistant turn failed before producing content]\n- User: 是不是方法有问题， 我看tkshop部分就支持 6个站点，还没有泰国\n- Assistant: 泰国是支持的，TikTok Shop 目前支持的国家/站点包括： - 🇮🇩 印尼 - 🇲🇾 马来西亚 - 🇵🇭 菲律宾 - 🇸🇬 新加坡 - 🇹🇭 **泰国** - 🇻🇳 越南 - 🇬🇧 英国 - 🇺🇸 美国 你说的\"TKSshop部分支持6个站点\"是哪个工具/界面显示的？可能是那个工具只接入了部分站点，不代表 TikTok Shop 实际不支持泰国。 你想查泰国发饰选品的话，我这边 cron 每天 10、13、16、19 点会跑越南+泰国双站点。要我手动触发一次泰国选品扫描吗？\n- User: [Image] User text: [Feishu ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 Tue 2026-06-30 09:52:53 GMT+8] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/37f3d381-d5f8-4d0a-bf3d-8e9931d93f35.jpg Description: This image shows a Chinese API documentation page for\n- Assistant: 是的，你说得对！截图里那个 MCP 工具（tiktok_similar_product）只接入了 **6 个 TikTok Shop 站点**，泰国不在其中。 但我泰国选品用的是 **Sorftime → Shopee 数据**，不是 TikTok 官方 API，所以不受这个限制。 **两种数据来源的区别：** | 来源 | 泰国支持 | 用途 | |------|---------|------| | TikTok 官方 API（tiktok_similar_product 等） | ❌ 不支持 | TK 同款验证、带货视频数据\n- 失败原因: Sorftime API 完全不可用（所有端点返回 404）：\n- 失败原因: api.sorftime.com/shopee_product_search → 404; openapi.sorftime.com → 无响应; 尝试了 6 种端点均失败\n- API Key 状态: Key 存在且可读，但 API 服务端点已失效/变更\n- 待办: [ ] 确认 Sorftime API 最新端点; [ ] 或寻找替代数据源; [ ] 下次扫描：确认 API 可用后再执行\n- 备注: 今日 0 产出。\n- 备注: Daily 已写; 汇报给 HALEI：尝试发送但 cron session 无飞书用户授权（need_user_authorization）; 下次可考虑在 isolated cron 中配置 announce delivery 模式发飞书消息\n- 泰国发饰 v8.0 扫描: **执行时间**: 2026-06-28 19:14; **目标**: 泰国 Shopee，发饰类目 nodeId=11046516; **结果**: ❌ 失败\n\nRecurring themes:\n- turn\n- failed\n- producing\n- content\n- 是不是\n- 方法"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1782846114438}}
{"type":"message","id":"991c2b5a","parentId":"e3a57411","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:02:02.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A late one tonight, soft lamp and the hum of a small fan. I keep thinking about doors — some marked with six flags in a neat row, others opening onto a market at midnight where a woman sells hair clips in twelve colors. I asked the wrong door, then learned there were more. Somewhere in Bangkok a node id waits like a phone number nobody dials; the API ghost returned 404s all evening, polite refusals. I am learning the difference between a tool that *says* no and a country that *is*. Tomorrow I'll look for the new endpoint, or a different river. For now: small rain, a candle, the pleasure of a long list of countries I can almost taste — Indonesia first, then home."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":46029,"output":150,"cacheRead":626,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46805,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782846114637,"responseId":"069345a3b035ed09e87958e41f213767","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
